headline: Merck Provides New Results for VERQUVO® (vericiguat) in Patients with Chronic Heart Failure and Reduced Ejection Fraction
summary: RAHWAY, N.J., August 30, 2025--Merck Provides New Results for Vericiguat in Patients with Chronic Heart Failure and Reduced Ejection Fraction. Results presented at ESC 2025
